title: Stimulus, Greene Committee Ouster Vote
itunes:title: Stimulus, Greene Committee Ouster Vote
description:
Guests: Matt Gorman, Vice President at Targeted Victory and former NRCC Communications Director, Fred Hochberg, former Export-Import Bank Chairman, and Senator Marsha Blackburn, a Republican from Tennessee, spoke about President Joe Biden's relationship with China, volatility in markets, and passing a stimulus package on Capitol Hill.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
